@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
}

<div class="container mt-5">
    <h1 class="text-center mb-4">About Us</h1>

    <!-- Slideshow -->
    <div id="aboutUsCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel" data-bs-interval="3000">
        <div class="carousel-inner">
            <!-- Image 1 -->
            <div class="carousel-item active">
                <img src="~/images/aboutus1.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="About Us 1">
            </div>
            <!-- Image 2 -->
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="~/images/aboutus2.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="About Us 2">
            </div>
            <!-- Image 3 -->
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="~/images/aboutus3.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="About Us 3">
            </div>
            <!-- Image 4 -->
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="~/images/aboutus4.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="About Us 4">
            </div>
            <!-- Image 5 -->
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="~/images/aboutus5.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="About Us 5">
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Carousel Controls -->
        <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#aboutUsCarousel" data-bs-slide="prev">
            <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
        </button>
        <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#aboutUsCarousel" data-bs-slide="next">
            <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
        </button>
    </div>

    <!-- Text Content -->
    <div class="mt-5">
        <h2>Our Story</h2>
        <p>
            Welcome to LostPaw! We started this journey with one simple goal: to help reunite lost pets with their owners and provide loving homes to animals in need. As pet lovers ourselves, we understand the pain of losing a pet, and we are committed to offering a platform where both lost and found pets can connect with the right people.
        </p>
        <p>
            Our platform began as a small community-driven initiative, but as word spread, it has grown into a trusted resource for pet owners all over the region. We have helped countless pets find their way home, and we continue to work tirelessly to make the world a better place for animals. Our commitment to animal welfare is at the heart of everything we do.
        </p>
        <p>
            Whether you're here to search for a lost pet or to give a furry friend a second chance, we welcome you with open arms. Our website is designed to make the process simple, quick, and reliable. We're constantly evolving, adding new features, and working with local shelters to provide as much support as possible.
        </p>

        <h3>Our Vision</h3>
        <p>
            At LostPaw, we envision a future where every lost pet is quickly reunited with its family, and every adoptable animal finds a loving home. Our vision goes beyond just helping individual animals; we strive to create a world where animal welfare is a priority, and where pets are treated with the care and respect they deserve.
        </p>
        <p>
            We believe in building a compassionate community of pet owners, rescue organizations, and volunteers who work together to improve the lives of animals everywhere. Our platform is designed to empower users to take control of their pets' well-being, while also providing educational resources to help prevent pet loss and abandonment.
        </p>
        <p>
            Our ultimate goal is to expand our reach, connect with even more pet lovers, and continue to make a meaningful impact on animal welfare globally. With your support, we can achieve this vision and make a lasting difference in the lives of pets and their owners. Thank you for being part of our community.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>
